---
title: Sesame Beef Stir Fry with Sugar Snap Peas and Basmati Rice
description: Traditional beef stir-fry is great, but this garlic, ginger, and hoisin concoction is seriously mind-blowing. It’s the perfect flavor and texture combination of tender meat, crispy veggies, and satisfying grains.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ginger-beef-stir-fry-w33-8860f837.jpg
